{{Quote|Star Wars has always been a part of my life, and was my first huge project back when my career started with Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic in 2006&hellip;It's awesome being part of the High Republic team, working alongside amazing writer Daniel, editors Elizabeth Brei and Riley Farmer, and Lucasfilm.|Harvey Tolibao|<ref name="IDW">{{SW|url=news/idw-star-wars-the-high-republic-adventures-announce|text=Yoda Returns With Another Lesson in IDW's ''Star Wars: The High Republic Adventures''}}</ref>}}
'''Harvey Tolibao''' pencilled [[Knights of the Old Republic 12|''Knights of the Old Republic'' 12]], [[Knights of the Old Republic 17|''Knights of the Old Republic'' 17]] and [[Knights of the Old Republic 18|''Knights of the Old Republic'' 18]]. He is also the penciller for [[Star Wars: The High Republic Adventures (2021)|''Star Wars: The High Republic Adventures'']]. His brother is [[Kevin Tolibao]].

